474
00:44:32,541 --> 00:44:33,791
Ela voa.

475
00:44:35,666 --> 00:44:37,625
Puxa. Puxa.

476
00:44:39,583 --> 00:44:40,958
Está cheio.

477
00:44:44,708 --> 00:44:45,958
